Package pers.yuyanzhou.bubblebobble.object.strategy

Class Gravity

java.lang.Object
pers.yuyanzhou.bubblebobble.object.strategy.Gravity
All Implemented Interfaces:
GameObject
Direct Known Subclasses:
GameChar, GameProp, Projectile
public abstract class Gravity extends Object implements GameObject
Gravity implements GameObject, Gravity is a game object whose coordinates change in the game world. Gravity integrates some common methods.
Author:
YuyanZhou
